          <name>SIBLING_ORDER</name>
          <briefdescription>
<para>Sets the sibling order of the actor so depth position can be defined within the same parent. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>Name &quot;siblingOrder&quot;, type <ref refid="classDali_1_1Property_1ab466e94d7adc55576e8e86ee96db565dac3c145c2e414f3ec168a6f4fb8968c5b" kindref="member">Property::INTEGER</ref>. <simplesect kind="note"><para>The initial value is 0. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Raise, Lower, RaiseToTop, LowerToBottom, RaiseAbove and LowerBelow will override the sibling order. The values set by this <ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1DevelActor_1_1Property" kindref="compound">Property</ref> will likely change. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
          </detaileddescription>
        </enumvalue>
